interactions.input_data: I need a comprehensive metabolic analysis of E. coli core model in the data/examples folder
interactions.output_data: These analyses show that the E. coli core model supports a growth rate of ~0.87 h⁻¹ on glucose minimal medium. Central glycolytic and TCA reactions (and their associated genes) are essential, while only a small subset of reactions exhibits flexibility at maximal biomass flux. No auxotrophies are detected. This comprehensive metabolic snapshot confirms robust carbon and energy metabolism within the core network.
